snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS III – LUCCA 2018 Tangled Trailer (Closed Captions)
snippet.description:
Find out more about KINGDOM HEARTS III: http://sqex.link/kingdd713a

Hurry and Pre-Order your KINGDOM HEARTS III Deluxe Edition before they’re all sold out! Supplies are limited! 
XB1 – sqex.link/kingda18ad
PS4 - sqex.link/kingd1f38e

Originally aired at Lucca Comics & Games, this trailer gives a sneak peek to magical Kingdom of Corona. Rapunzel leaves her mysterious tower for the first time with the help of charming bandit Flynn Rider. Sora, Donald and Goofy join the pair on their journey to the kingdom, taking on the Heartless along the way.

KINGDOM HEARTS III is coming to Microsoft Xbox One and Sony PlayStation® 4 on January 29, 2019.
